Manage Page Groups

Use page groupings to create sumarised view of sections of your website. Read more...

The group pages functionality allows for multiple pages of a similar type to be categorized together under a single group name. This allows for key performance metrics and user behavior to analysed, both on an individual group of pages, and comparison between different groups of pages. More information can be found on the Netbiscuits Knowledge Base.
